              "id": "bebbdeb7",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"83\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"83\">Commercial Hard Surface Restoration &amp; Maintenance That Protects Your Investment</strong></h2><p data-start=\"85\" data-end=\"286\">In business, your floors do more than support daily operations. They represent your brand. Worn, dull, or damaged hard surfaces can create the wrong first impression for clients, tenants, and visitors.</p><p data-start=\"288\" data-end=\"461\">At Midland Floor Care, we provide specialized commercial hard surface restoration and maintenance services that bring your floors back to peak condition and keep them there.</p><p data-start=\"463\" data-end=\"499\"><strong data-start=\"463\" data-end=\"499\">Surfaces we restore and maintain</strong></p><ul data-start=\"500\" data-end=\"893\"><li data-start=\"500\" data-end=\"564\"><p data-start=\"502\" data-end=\"564\">Stone floors: marble, granite, terrazzo, limestone, and more</p></li><li data-start=\"565\" data-end=\"644\"><p data-start=\"567\" data-end=\"644\">Tile and grout: ceramic, porcelain, and natural stone in high traffic areas</p></li><li data-start=\"645\" data-end=\"725\"><p data-start=\"647\" data-end=\"725\">Concrete: polished, stained, or sealed in warehouses, showrooms, and lobbies</p></li><li data-start=\"726\" data-end=\"817\"><p data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"817\">Luxury vinyl and VCT: stripping, waxing, burnishing, and sealing for long lasting shine</p></li><li data-start=\"818\" data-end=\"893\"><p data-start=\"820\" data-end=\"893\">Specialty flooring: unique materials that need expert care and protection</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"895\" data-end=\"932\"><strong data-start=\"895\" data-end=\"932\">Why commercial floor care matters</strong></p><ul data-start=\"933\" data-end=\"1229\"><li data-start=\"933\" data-end=\"996\"><p data-start=\"935\" data-end=\"996\">Preserve your image: spotless floors signal professionalism</p></li><li data-start=\"997\" data-end=\"1080\"><p data-start=\"999\" data-end=\"1080\">Extend floor life: reduce replacement costs by protecting structure and surface</p></li><li data-start=\"1081\" data-end=\"1164\"><p data-start=\"1083\" data-end=\"1164\">Enhance safety: anti slip treatments and deep cleaning support safety standards</p></li><li data-start=\"1165\" data-end=\"1229\"><p data-start=\"1167\" data-end=\"1229\">Minimize downtime: flexible scheduling keeps operations moving</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1231\" data-end=\"1274\"><strong data-start=\"1231\" data-end=\"1274\">Our restoration and maintenance process</strong></p><ol data-start=\"1275\" data-end=\"1761\"><li data-start=\"1275\" data-end=\"1357\"><p data-start=\"1278\" data-end=\"1357\">On site assessment: evaluate traffic patterns, materials, and existing damage</p></li><li data-start=\"1358\" data-end=\"1422\"><p data-start=\"1361\" data-end=\"1422\">Custom service plan: tailored to your flooring and schedule</p></li><li data-start=\"1423\" data-end=\"1514\"><p data-start=\"1426\" data-end=\"1514\">Deep cleaning and stain removal: equipment that lifts embedded soil and restores color</p></li><li data-start=\"1515\" data-end=\"1614\"><p data-start=\"1518\" data-end=\"1614\">Restoration or refinishing: smooths the surface and brings back luster while adding protection</p></li><li data-start=\"1615\" data-end=\"1687\"><p data-start=\"1618\" data-end=\"1687\">Sealing or coating: barrier against stains, scratches, and moisture</p></li><li data-start=\"1688\" data-end=\"1761\"><p data-start=\"1691\" data-end=\"1761\">Ongoing maintenance program: keeps floors in peak condition year round</p></li></ol><p data-start=\"1763\" data-end=\"1786\"><strong data-start=\"1763\" data-end=\"1786\">Industries we serve</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1787\" data-end=\"1990\"><li data-start=\"1787\" data-end=\"1825\"><p data-start=\"1789\" data-end=\"1825\">Corporate offices and headquarters</p></li><li data-start=\"1826\" data-end=\"1859\"><p data-start=\"1828\" data-end=\"1859\">Hotels and hospitality venues</p></li><li data-start=\"1860\" data-end=\"1898\"><p data-start=\"1862\" data-end=\"1898\">Retail stores and shopping centers</p></li><li data-start=\"1899\" data-end=\"1924\"><p data-start=\"1901\" data-end=\"1924\">Healthcare facilities</p></li><li data-start=\"1925\" data-end=\"1953\"><p data-start=\"1927\" data-end=\"1953\">Schools and universities</p></li><li data-start=\"1954\" data-end=\"1990\"><p data-start=\"1956\" data-end=\"1990\">Government and municipal buildings</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1992\" data-end=\"2036\"><strong data-start=\"1992\" data-end=\"2036\">Why businesses choose Midland Floor Care</strong></p><ul data-start=\"2037\" data-end=\"2293\"><li data-start=\"2037\" data-end=\"2081\"><p data-start=\"2039\" data-end=\"2081\">Expertise across multiple flooring types</p></li><li data-start=\"2082\" data-end=\"2165\"><p data-start=\"2084\" data-end=\"2165\">Commercial grade equipment and products for better results and faster dry times</p></li><li data-start=\"2166\" data-end=\"2235\"><p data-start=\"2168\" data-end=\"2235\">Flexible service hours: nights, weekends, and off peak scheduling</p></li><li data-start=\"2236\" data-end=\"2293\"><p data-start=\"2238\" data-end=\"2293\">Satisfaction guaranteed with our Midland Shine Standard</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"2295\" data-end=\"2489\"><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/schedule-a-visit/\"><strong data-start=\"2295\" data-end=\"2324\">Schedule an on-site visit</strong></a><br data-start=\"2324\" data-end=\"2327\" />Ready to protect your brand and your floors. Call us or request an on-site visit, and we\u2019ll walk the space, map priorities, and deliver a clear plan and timeline.</p><p data-start=\"2491\" data-end=\"2519\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Thank you,<br data-start=\"2501\" data-end=\"2504\" />Justin Campbell</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/covid19-protected-services/\">COVID-19 Protected</a></li><li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/the-secret-to-floor-care-for-various-materials/\">The Secret to Floor Care for Various Materials</a></li><li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/the-top-methods-for-cost-effective-floor-maintenance/\">The Top Methods for Cost-Effective Floor Maintenance</a></li><li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/ultimate-guide-to-floor-care-for-retail/\">Ultimate Guide to Floor Care for Retail</a></li><li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/7-essential-tips-for-impeccable-commercial-floor-care-services/\">7 Essential Tips for Impeccable Commercial Floor Care Services</a></li></ul>",
